{"tid":2083074,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"SEA TO SKY加推238伙 研內地客視像揀樓","createTime":"2020-06-28T13:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T04:01:31.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"583a469e1f02d4af2bd78cd8bf1f7fb4f93ec6f6","tid":2083074,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"SEA TO SKY加推238伙 研內地客視像揀樓<br />\n4 小時前<br />\n<br />\n長江實業集團(1113)將軍澳日出康城第8期「SEA TO SKY」昨進行首輪銷售462伙，據市場消息指，單位接近沽清。發展商即「添食」加推第3號價單，涉238伙，折實平均呎價16,599元，較第2號價單輕微提價0.4%，若較1號價單計則高近5%。<br />\n<br />\n（已節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2/sea-to-sky%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8238%E4%BC%99-%E7%A0%94%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%8F%80%E6%A8%93-224476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%2Fsea-to-sky%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A8238%25E4%25BC%2599-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%258F%2580%25E6%25A8%2593-224476&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=a11b6efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2/sea-to-sky%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8238%E4%BC%99-%E7%A0%94%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%96%E5%83%8F%E6%8F%80%E6%A8%93-224476</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">視像揀樓如果能落實，長實在賣樓方面創了香港地產界先河</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c69f1692bf61446f340d44b142ccfc95137dc9","tid":2083074,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"Property Panda"}]}